## Markov Chain Attribution


::: {.cell flg_pro='false'}

```{.r .cell-code}
markov_model_result <- markov_model(
  Data = channel_stack,
  var_path = "path",
  var_conv = "conversion",
  var_null = "non_conversion",
  out_more = TRUE
)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```

